title: Elves Clan: Tricky Adventures
description: Elves Clan: Tricky Adventures it's a wild platformer game where you've got to help Triki, Friki, and Kiki get to Chicho's house. But be ready, because everything from platforms to obstacles is out to get you. Snag some unusual coins and Tricky-Piranhas to help you out. It's easy to start, but oh boy, it's a tough one to master. These cheeky elves are up to some pranks, and they need your hand. Are you ready for the challenge?
